title: Community
---
body:

Working with Spyder is more fun when you can ask questions to other users.

Here is where you can find other Spyder users:

* [Find us on Stack Overflow](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/spyder)
* [Ask us a question on Stack Overflow](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/ask?tags=spyder)
* [Chat with us on Gitter](https://gitter.im/spyder-ide/public) (spyder-ide/public)
* [Open an issue on Github](https://github.com/spyder-ide/spyder/issues/new)


Want to get in contact with us otherwise?

* [Follow us via Twitter at @Spyder_IDE](https://twitter.com/Spyder_IDE)
* [Like us on Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/SpyderIDE/)
* [Join our Google+ Community](https://plus.google.com/u/0/communities/112932801653352854842)
